methods.get:
Gets the value associated with the key

:param key: (AssociativeData.KEY) - key
:return: (AssociativeData.VALUE) value associated with the key
methods.isModifiable:
Whether the dataset is modifiable.

:return: (boolean) true if the dataset is modifiable, false if not
methods.put:
Adds the key-value pair to the dataset.

:param key: (AssociativeData.KEY) - key
:param value: (AssociativeData.VALUE) - value
methods.putAll:
Adds all key-value pairs in the map to the dataset.

Note: Java generics information - <K extends AssociativeData.KEY,
V extends AssociativeData.VALUE>

:param values: (java.util.Map<K,V>) - keypair map

text: Dataset which has values associated with keys.
